# Bug Report

## Summary
When the "Message" field is left empty in the contact form on the Tendable website, no error message is displayed when click on submit button.

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Navigate to https://www.tendable.com
2. Fill in the "Name", "Subject", and "Phone" fields.
3. Leave the "Message" field empty.
4. Click the "Submit" button.

## Expected Result
An error message should be displayed when the field blank.

## Actual Result
No error message is displayed.
